âDonât you think youâve stretched that neck of yours just about enough?
Itâs unhealthy, you know.  The mateâs gone, so I canât afford to lose you
too.  You must be very, very careful of your health, Cooky.  Understand?â

His last word, in striking contrast with the smoothness of his previous
