âLook at âim run!  Look at âim run!â I could hear him crying.  âAnâ with
a gyme leg at that!  Come on back, you pore little mammaâs darling.  I
wonât âit yer; no, I wonât.â

I came back and went on with my work; and here the episode ended for the
time, though further developments were yet to take place.  I set the
