âDeath Larsen!â I involuntarily cried.  âIs he like you?â

âHardly.  He is a lump of an animal without any head.  He has all myâmyââ

âBrutishness,â I suggested.

âYes,âthank you for the word,âall my brutishness, but he can scarcely
