   âWhat, without asking, hither hurried _Whence_?
   And, without asking, _Whither_ hurried hence!
      Oh, many a Cup of this forbidden Wine
   Must drown the memory of that insolence!â

âGreat!â Wolf Larsen cried.  âGreat!  Thatâs the keynote.  Insolence!  He
