continued to gaze silently and curiously.

Leach had worked himself into an ecstasy of impotent rage.

âPig!  Pig!  Pig!â he was reiterating at the top of his lungs.  âWhy
donât you come down and kill me, you murderer?  You can do it!  I ainât
