âLucky for me he doesnât carry a searchlight,â Wolf Larsen said.

âWhat if I should cry out loudly?â I queried in a whisper.

âIt would be all up,â he answered.  âBut have you thought upon what would
immediately happen?â

Before I had time to express any desire to know, he had me by the throat
