âI wish it werenât so late,â I said.  âIâd like to see how it works.â

âDonât be a glutton, Humphrey,â Maud chided me.  âRemember, to-morrow is
coming, and youâre so tired now that you can hardly stand.â

âAnd you?â I said, with sudden solicitude.  âYou must be very tired.  You
